OL,3,CAndy Burnham invites fellow Everton
OL,4,Cfan Canadian PM Mark Carney to match
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has invited fellow
OL,7,FEverton fan and Prime Minister Mark
OL,8,FCarney to watch a game with him at the
OL,9,Fnew Hill Dickinson Stadium in the
OL,10,Ffuture.
OL,12,FMr Carney adopted Everton as his team
OL,13,Fafter moving to the UK to be Bank of
OL,14,FEngland governor, while Mr Burnham has
OL,15,Fbeen an Evertonian all his life and
OL,16,Fhas a season ticket.
OL,18,FThe Prime Ministers spoke on Wednesday
OL,19,F22 July about their countries' "strong
OL,20,Fand strategic relationship".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
