OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784834319
OL,3,CAndy Burnham invites fellow Everton
OL,4,Cfan Canadian PM Mark Carney to match
OL,6,FA Downing Street spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Prime Minister Carney congratulated
OL,8,Fthe Prime Minister on his appointment,
OL,9,Fand the leaders discussed the Prime
OL,10,FMinister's strong domestic
OL,11,Fannouncements in recent days to give
OL,12,Fthe British people breathing space
OL,13,Ffrom the cost of living.
OL,15,F"The UK and Canada had a strong and
OL,16,Fstrategic relationship, rooted in
OL,17,Fshared values and outlook on the
OL,18,Fworld, which benefitted people in both
OL,19,Fcountries, the leaders agreed."
