OL,3,CAndy Burnham invites fellow Everton
OL,4,Cfan Canadian PM Mark Carney to match
OL,6,F"As fellow Everton fans, the Prime
OL,7,FMinister said he hoped to be able to
OL,8,Froll out the blue carpet and host
OL,9,FPrime Minister Carney at an Everton
OL,10,Fgame in the future," she added.
OL,12,FThe former Greater Manchester Mayor
OL,13,Fhas pledged to lead a "cost-of-living
OL,14,Fgovernment" during his first Cabinet
OL,15,Fmeeting on Tuesday 21 July.
OL,17,FHis policies so far have included
OL,18,Fcutting VAT on energy bills, capping
OL,19,Fbus fares at #2, and now the reduction
OL,20,Fof business rates on pubs, clubs and
OL,21,Fmusic venues.
